## Expand / Collapse Behaviour

### Widths

| State | Column width | Island visible width |
|---|---|---|
| Expanded | 252px | 232px |
| Collapsed | 68px | 48px |

### Toggle button

- Positioned in the top area of the island (replaces/joins the current dark-mode toggle).
- Renders a `ChevronLeft` icon when expanded, `ChevronRight` when collapsed.
- `aria-label`: `"Collapse sidebar"` / `"Expand sidebar"`.
- `aria-expanded`: reflects current state on the button.
- The branding row (logo + name) is always rendered; in collapsed state the name and
  strapline are hidden (opacity 0 + width 0) but the `BrandMark` icon remains visible.

### Persistence

```ts
const SIDEBAR_KEY = "riskshield.sidebar.collapsed";

// Read on mount
const [isCollapsed, setIsCollapsed] = useState<boolean>(() => {
  try { return localStorage.getItem(SIDEBAR_KEY) === "1"; }
  catch { return false; }
});

// Write on toggle
const toggle = () => {
  const next = !isCollapsed;
  setIsCollapsed(next);
  try { localStorage.setItem(SIDEBAR_KEY, next ? "1" : "0"); } catch { /* ignore */ }
};
```

