## Accessibility

| Requirement | Implementation |
|---|---|
| Toggle has `aria-label` | `aria-label="Collapse sidebar"` / `"Expand sidebar"` |
| Toggle has `aria-expanded` | `aria-expanded={!isCollapsed}` |
| Collapsed nav item labels readable | Label `<span>` remains in DOM, `aria-hidden` is NOT set — screen readers read them |
| Search hidden from AT when collapsed | `aria-hidden="true"` on search wrapper when collapsed |
| Focus ring on toggle | `outline: 2px solid var(--brand)` on `:focus-visible` via `<style>` tag |
| Nav keyboard traversal | Unchanged — `NavLink` handles focus naturally |

